Dialogs.Dialog: Rinko
What are you doing ▲主人公＊▲？
Well, I guess it's just a walk in the park, ▲小早川＊▲.
Hmm. In other words, you were just wandering around with no particular purpose.
Okay, Rinko is going now.
Okay. I'm going to hang around some more before I go home.
Ah, ▲小早川＊▲！
Rinko
You startled me. Why are you here？
I was checking out the place. I was wondering if there was a good place for a date.
You mean... A date with Rinko, right？
Isn't it obvious？ I'll find you a nice place.
Hehe, better not ask for more details then. Bye.
Rinko
Hehe, surprised you, ▲主人公＊▲？
I was really surprised... Why are you here ▲小早川＊▲？
My little brother begged me to come over and play.
Where's your brother？
He found a friend and they are playing over there. His friend's mom said she'd watch my brother with me, so Rinko went for a little walk.
Well, I'd better get back.
Yeah. See you.
Rinko
I thought I saw a familiar rear view...
Ah, are you alone, ▲小早川＊▲？
My dad's keeping me company today. He said, 'I really have to see the movie." I told him to go by himself.
Parents and children should be able to be together... And what about your father？
He's over there watching a movie, okay？ Rinko came out of the movie because it was boring. Well, I'd better get back.
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
Odd. Come to see a movie, ▲小早川＊▲？
Nah. I just came by because I found a brochure I wanted.
I see. So, did you buy it？
Yup. It's a gift because my mom's favorite actor is in it.
(They must be closer now.)
Huh？ Come to see a movie, ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko
Yes. But I stopped.
Why？
My little brother called me up and spoiled me by saying, "Come home early and play with me~."
Haha, I see. You're being a good onee-chan.
Rinko
Hmm, are you trying to muscle up？
Ah！ Are you training too, ▲小早川＊▲？
No way. Just passing by... Maybe hoping you were here？
I see. Glad to hear it.
Just a hunch... Stop grinning.
Huh, what are you doing, ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko
Oh, I'm just getting to the right place. Do you know if the swimming school here is reputable？
Reputation？ I don't know, but... Why？
My little brother wants to learn. So, Rinko is going to scout the area, and I'm going to give that role to you.
It's a heavy load for me, I'm declining.
You don't have to hold back. Well, I'll leave it to you.
(And so she says...)
Rinko
You come here to exercise, ▲主人公＊▲？
Yo... Yeah, you know how sometimes you just have an urge to exercise, ▲小早川＊▲？
I don't.
You don't, huh.
I don't. I do have times when I feel the urge to read a book without a second thought, though... Oh, I feel like reading. I'm going home now.
(You didn't have any business around here then.)
Rinko
Hehe, I knew it was you.
Ah, you were here too. Are you out shopping ▲小早川＊▲？
Maybe, yeah... What are you going to buy when you come all the way down here？ You're not buying a can of mackerel, are you？
No way. It's just window shopping.
Then you should have invited me... Well, I can't because I still have things to do.
(So you have an errant to run, huh...)
What a coincidence, ▲小早川＊▲！
Rinko
...Unfortunately, you're not the guy Rinko's looking for right now...
What！？
My little brother got lost and I'm looking for him.
Ah, mom.
Hello... Yes, ah, you found him？ Yes, I understand. Later.
They found my little brother... Okay, I'm off then.
I see, good for you. Bye- bye.
Rinko
What are you doing alone ▲主人公＊▲？
I'm just looking around. You're not alone, are you ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko was on her father's errand. Suddenly, he asked me to get the shoes he ordered. He said he really needed them today.
I see, sounds tough.
Honestly, he's a very caring father...
Rinko
Wow... why are you here？
I was really surprised. What are you doing, ▲小早川＊▲！？
Nothing. I was just passing by. Were you interested in today's event？
Hmmm... maybe, maybe not.
So you just came here at random because you're free？ But too bad, Rinko is too busy to bother you, bye.
Rinko
Did you come to see what it's all about, ▲主人公＊▲？
Yo！ I guess so. And you, ▲小早川＊▲？
Yeah, I came here because I heard a rumor that they were doing a Volvavin show... Looks like it was a false alarm.
You will watch it？ Not your little brother, ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko promised to watch it for him and recreate it for him in real life. Well, my little brother is waiting for me, so I'm going home.
(A realistic recreation... So, you wanted to watch it, ▲小早川＊▲.)
(Huh... Is that you, ▲小早川＊▲？)
▲小早川＊▲！
Rinko
Don't yell so loud, ▲主人公＊▲.
You looking for someone？
Yes, I think I saw a musician visiting Japan, but I lost him.
Haha, you're a chaperone. So you're also like that, ▲小早川＊▲...
What.
...It's nothing.
Rinko
Good, a winning streak！
You came to play, ▲小早川＊▲？
Well, yeah, I have to give these guys a rub once in a while.
I see, be careful.
It's all right. Well, then, the challenger is here. See you later.
Yo. What a coincidence. Wanna play together ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko
I can't right now... I just got a call from a friend and we're meeting now, ▲主人公＊▲.
I see... Bad timing.
I don't want people to say, "Rinko is all about boyfriends and neglects her friends." You don't want that either, do you？
(Yeah, I'd rather have a girlfriend who cares about her friends.)
Rinko
Alone in an arcade, ▲主人公＊▲？
You caught me. Well... I thought I'd sneak in some practice.
You can tell Rinko that and I'll coach you.
That doesn't make sense. I want to practice on my own and surprise you, ▲小早川＊▲.
Hmm. Well, I'll be waiting with anticipation. Rinko is always open to challenges.
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
Ah, ▲小早川＊▲.
Were you ever interested in electrical appliances？
Not that I'm interested in it. I often look at it, thinking how useful it would be if I had it at home, don't you？
The electronics section. Rinko has some business on the other floor, so I'm sorry, but I have to go.
(It's probably the video games or the AV equipment section...)
▲小早川＊▲.
Rinko
Oh, you're here too？ You are here to kill time？
Don't assume that I'm just killing time. You're not wrong... what about you, ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko came here because she had something to do. She didn't come here because she was free.
An errand？
Family service, you know. It's also a daughter's duty.
(Sounds like a salaryman.)
Rinko
Onii-san, now you can get 20% back in points.
Wow！ ...You surprised me.
Hehe... Rinko was surprised when she found you too.
Shopping？
No, I'm killing time until I go to dinner with my family. I'll meet them near here soon.
I see, go have fun.
Ah, ▲小早川＊▲！
Rinko
Oh, what. What's wrong？
I don't have anything to do...
I see. Rinko is busy checking imports right now, so don't bother me.
I see, I'm interrupting you.
No, I'm sorry.
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
Yo.
You should be a little more surprised that we bumped into each other.
Haha, I'm not surprised to see you at all now.
....By the way, is this the Western music section？
I guess... I'm looking into it？
That's a good attitude. If you have any questions, just ask. I'll teach you everything I know.
Rinko
Whoa...
Ah, it's you. What are you doing around here, ▲小早川＊▲？
What I'm doing here, you ask... well, this a CD store... and it's normal for Rinko to be here.
But this is the J-Pop section, remember？
Um... my little brother... Oh, right, there was a song my that little brother liked, so I came to look for it. See you.
(Really？)
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
You came here too, ▲小早川＊▲？
No, I was just passing by. Anyway, are you a... lolicon？
Why would I be！
Hmm, no？
No, it's not！
I thought it was obvious since you are standing proudly in front of a poster of a beautiful girl.
(Coincidence...)
Rinko
Nice place... Hey, are you a regular here？ Do you know the waitress ▲主人公＊▲？
I don't think so. What's wrong？
I found a toy that my brother wanted, and I was wondering if I could ask you to keep it or something.
I see, a rare one？ I'll order it then.
Really？ Yay, that's a big help.
Huh, do you come often to the anime shop, ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko
Whenever I have business in this area, I take a peek. Sometimes I find cute cat goods.
Oh, I see. Did you find a good one today？
I didn't find much today. I don't have time to look for them carefully.
Well, I'll check out too.
Hehe, thank you.
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
Ah. What are you doing here ▲小早川＊▲！？
Rinko is just passing through. I've got some stuff to do, so I can't relax...
I see. Well, why don't you go now？
Your panicky attitude is suspicious.
I'm not panicking... Look, you have something to do. Don't you have to go？
I'd go without being told. I knew it was suspicious. Well, that's fine.
Rinko
Are you going to enter this shop by any chance, ▲主人公＊▲？
Eh！？ Yes... I might as well try to get in, haha.
If you want to go in, just go in with an open mind.
It's not that I really want to go in... weren't you planning to go somewhere ▲小早川＊▲？
Ah, that's right. Honestly, it's just because you're in a strange place.
(I wasn't holding you back...)
Rinko
"Please come home soon, Master ▼"... like this？
What are you doing ▲小早川＊▲！？
I was wondering if I could get a part-time job. This store sometimes holds a cat ear event. On those days, the staff all wear cat ears.
A part-time job！？ You, ▲小早川＊▲？
...Of course it's a lie. You know Rinko hates customer service, right？ Well, I've got to go.
(I'm relieved...)
Rinko
You're very religious.
Whoa... I'm not religious, I just wanted to come to a quiet place, ▲小早川＊▲.
I see. Well, Rinko likes it too, so I can understand how you feel.
You also came to freshen up ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko came to immerse herself in reading. When I'm at home, I'm worried about my little brother... So, you better don't distract me.
Okay...
(Hanging around here, what's going on ▲小早川＊▲？)
(Oops, lost her！)
▲小早川＊▲！
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
What were you doing？
I was looking for a kitten because I heard its voice. Did she hide from me？
I know！ If I have milk or something, I might just grab her... Okay, I'm going back to get it. Bye-bye.
(In a way, you've been busy...)
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
Yo, ▲小早川＊▲.
A leisurely stroll？
Yeah, something like that. What about you ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko was taking a walk too. But I just got a call from my dad, so I have to go.
I see. Let's come back to relax together next time.
Rinko
Bowling alone, ▲主人公＊▲？
Yes！ I just thought it might be nice once in a while.
I see. So your girlfriend won't ask you out？
You want to go out with me？ Then let's do it together now.
Too bad. Rinko has something important to do.
...I knew it.
Are you going somewhere ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko
Oh, I guess. I have an appointment with a friend.
By the way, what's so fun about bowling？ You just roll the ball toward the distance.
You don't just roll it. You hit the pins and knock them over...
...You don't always hit the pins. That's why...
(That's up to practice...)
Rinko
Oh, I found a lonely looking boy.
You say I look lonely... I think I'm having fun, ▲小早川＊▲.
I don't see it that way, do you？
Then go out with me.
Rinko has some errands to run... Well, I'll watch you for a bit. Hang in there.
All right！
Rinko
What are you doing ▲主人公＊▲？
Um...
Perhaps a one-man karaoke？
Um, yeah... that might be a good idea too.
Hmmm. Well, I hear there's quite a large population of hitokara. I guess it's not so bad.
(I'm glad I don't look like an idiot...)
▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko
Oh, it's you. Are you going to karaoke？
Yeah... What about you？ If you're free, why don't you come with me ▲小早川＊▲？
Unfortunately, I don't have time for this. Invite me next time you're free.
I see. I'll see you next time.
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
That's a great coincidence, ▲小早川＊▲.
Really？ We don't live that far from each other. The places we go for fun are usually the same.
Well, yes. That makes you happy, doesn't it？
Yeah... I don't know about that.
Rinko
Aren't you supposed to come to these places with your girlfriend？
▲小早川＊▲！
Hehe. That girlfriend of yours is here！
Who did you come with, ▲小早川＊▲？
With my family. But my little brother fell asleep, and we had to go home.
I see. It's like a family reunion.
(Ah, there she is. It seems you're talking to someone ▲小早川＊▲.)
(Ah, I guess they're done talking.)
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
What, you noticed me？ Who were you talking to？
Some strangers.
Eh？
They asked me to help them with a survey, and I said no.
You all right？
Well, Rinko is an adult and won't kick you right away if you persist.
(I guess that's true...)
Do you like these places enough to come alone ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko
My friend invited me out. She said it was a preview of our date.
I see. I'd like to check it out.
Not today. We're women, and we're going to plan a date from a woman's point of view.
A spot from a woman's point of view...
Are you thinking something weird？ Well, it's fine, bye.
Rinko
Where are you going ▲主人公＊▲？
Yo！ Hey, I thought I could have a cup of tea here.
I see. The new desserts here have a reputation for being very tasty.
Hmm. Want to eat together？
I would love to go, but not today. Let me know what you think after you try them.
Going somewhere？ ▲小早川＊▲！
Rinko
Just a bit. By the way, are you the type of person who likes to have tea alone ▲主人公＊▲？
I'm not sure I like it, but... Well, so-so.
Hmm, don't cry just because you're lonely. I'll go out with you the next time your girlfriend is free.
I see, you're busy.
Well yeah, see you.
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
Yo. You alone？
Just for now. I have an appointment with a friend. What about you？
I'm free, so I thought I'd have a cup of tea.
Why don't you just drink that stuff at home？
It tastes different than if you put it in yourself.
I see, I don't mind then. Well, take your time.
▲小早川＊▲.
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
What's up？ You want some tea？
No, I was just passing by. I have to go home now.
I see. I'm sorry I held you back.
Okay, no problem. I'll see you later.
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
You came for tea, ▲小早川＊▲？
No, I have some business nearby. Do you take tea alone？
Yes.
I see. That's kind of mature, isn't it？
Are you falling in love with me all over again？
Idiot.
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
I knew it was you.... Hehe. Eating out？
Yeah, I guess eating out all the time isn't good for you.
In your case, it would be better for your health to eat out than to eat only canned mackerel at home.
...I don't eat only canned mackerel, though.
At least order with nutritional balance in mind. See you later.
▲小早川＊▲！
Rinko
Ah. Dinner at this restaurant today？
Yes, I like the taste of this place.
I see, really？
But you make it better, ▲小早川＊▲.
Idiot. Are you trying to flatter me？ I'm leaving.
Rinko
Where are you going？
Wow... you surprised me. Where are you going, ▲小早川＊▲？
Rinko is having dinner with her family. Dad said he has time today, which is rare.
I see. But aren't we together now？
We'll meet there. I'm off then.
Yeah, see ya.
Rinko
I like it. You're eating alone at your leisure...
It's better to eat with the family than alone, right, ▲小早川＊▲？
That's not true. I'm told to eat my vegetables and my little brother gets to take my favorite side dish...
That's a childish reason. Your mom makes great food, doesn't she？
Yeah, I guess. Well, that's why I'm going home for a nice dinner.
(What a surprise, you're happy with it.)
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
Just in time. I'm thinking of going out to dinner now, would you like to join me ▲小早川＊▲？
Too bad... Rinko just ate a while ago.
Well, I will eat and you can have tea and a dessert, ▲小早川＊▲...
Sorry, I promised to go to my friend's house now.
I see... I guess I'll give up then.
Sorry, maybe another time.
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
Whassup.
Maybe you knew Rinko was around here somewhere？
No way. It's just a coincidence.
Well, I'd better get going.
See ya.
Rinko
Huh... why are you here？
If you're asking me why, I'll tell you... but first why are you here？
Geez. I asked the question first, so the rule is that you answer first.
I was... taking a walk！
So, you're free. Rinko was... Oh, no！ I'm going to be late. See you later！
(But you didn't answer my question...)
Rinko
Sorry to keep you waiting.
Did we have a meet-up ▲小早川＊▲！？
Hehe, nope. I saw you, so I thought I'd surprise you.
So that was it... I was nervous about forgetting a promise.
If you forget your real promise, I'll kick you mercilessly.
(I'll be careful...)
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
Yo, what a coincidence, ▲小早川＊▲.
Isn't it a bit like being tied by a red string when you bump into someone you haven't promised to meet？
Yeah, I think so.
I-I was just kidding. If you say it with a straight face like that, I would be embarrassed...
Since we're here, do you want to go on a date？
Nope！ Rinko has plans. See you later.
(And she's gone...)
Rinko
Ah...
Ah.
Coincidence, right？ It's kind of weird...
Really. I'm both happy and embarrassed.
Hehe, we've talked too much. I've got to go.
I see. I'll see you later.
(I'm free...)
Rinko
You're in a daze, ▲主人公＊▲...
Ah, it's you. Perhaps you have some free time, ▲小早川＊▲？
Do I look like that？ Unfortunately, I have to leave now.
Not quite as expected.
Hmm？
I'll go this way. Well, I'll see you later.
Rinko
▲主人公＊▲.
Hehe... I had a feeling I was going to meet you.
Hmm. I was thinking that, too.
Really？ I don't remember you being that good.
Are you okay on time？
Oh, I have to go now... Bye-bye.
Bye-bye.
Hey, ▲小早川＊▲！
Rinko
Ah.
Are you alone？
Yeah. Just a little something to do. My mom's taking care of my little brother.
Do you want me to accompany you？
It's okay, it's not a big deal. I'd feel bad. See you later.
Yeah, see ya.
(That's a fancy dress...)
Rinko
You saw that woman just now...
Well, there's a reason, ▲小早川＊▲！
You didn't even notice Rinko was this close to you...
I just happened to be in a daze.
I see. Well, it's fine... See you, Rinko is in a hurry.
Yes, bye-bye.
(I was surprised, but... I convinced her, right？)
Rinko
Hiya！ Small kick.
Ouch！
You are full of openings.
I knew it was you, ▲小早川＊▲.
...I've got to go to. I have an appointment with a friend.
See you later.
